reviewText: THIS SERMON SPEAKS ABOUT LIFE'S SET BACK'S AND HOW IT HAPPENS TO US AT UNEXPECTED TIME'S BUT IT'S ONLY TEMPORARY ON OUR ROAD TO DESTINY. 2 DVDS
If you are having major problems this is a must for you. It wil help you to understand that He has not given up on you & that you are not alone in even in the hardest times of your life.
